snippet.title: SNES A Day 82: Roger Clemens' MVP Baseball
snippet.description:
Review: https://snesaday.com/2014/08/15/82-roger-clemens-mvp-baseball/

Roger Clemens' MVP Baseball doesn't seem like a very good baseball game. I can't get over how bad throwing the ball feels!
